<P>
   ONLINE-ASTROLOGER-MEDIA (Undated) _ Profile of the online
astrologist Susie Miller, whose Web site has become so popular that
a flurry of other media deals have followed: television
commentaries on shows like Fox5's Good Morning New York, a book
contract, columns in magazines like McCall's, Self, and Modern
Bride. In two years, purely through word of mouth, she has garnered
a mailing list of 30,000 devoted readers. And now Infoseek is about
to make her its designated astrologist. By Lisa Napoli.
</P>
