   - The safety factor: &UR; Corey Wade &LR; , whose real name is  &UR; Gabriel &LR; 
 &UR; Macharia &LR;  and who is a former security guard for  &UR; Sylvester &LR; 
 &UR; Stallone &LR; , was sentenced to 25 years in prison for trying to kill
another Stallone security guard and trying to steal a $25,000 sword
from the boss. Wade shot the victim five times, slashed his throat
and beat him with a baton, but he survived.
</P>
